[metadata]

Name:Test - Macro Replay - Saffi Titan Altar
URL:https://www.cardforge.org

Goal:Win

Turns:1

Difficulty:Rare

Description:Test puzzle for replaying a delayed recursion loop: Saffi Eriksdotter plus Sun Titan plus Altar of Dementia. The graveyard includes extra Sun Titan-legal permanents so replay must consistently select Saffi. Record one cycle that sacrifices Saffi targeting Sun Titan, sacrifices Sun Titan to Altar of Dementia targeting the opponent, returns Sun Titan, then uses Sun Titan's trigger to return Saffi from the graveyard. Repeat until the opponent has no library, then cast Sign in Blood targeting the opponent.

